===============================================================================
[ Description ]

  odbc_field_num(Odbc\Result $statement, string $field): int|false~

Gets the number of the column slot that corresponds to the named field in the
given result object.

===============================================================================
[ Parameters ]

{statement}

  The ODBC result object.

{field}

  The field name.

===============================================================================
[ Return Values ]

Returns the field number as a integer, or false on error. Field numbering
starts at 1.

